==Awards and honors==
*Captain: [[Paul G. Goebel]]
*All-Americans: Paul G. Goebel (selected by ''[[Athletic World]]'' based on votes of 250 coaches), [[Harry Kipke]] (selected by [[Walter Camp]], ''Athletic World'' and [[Walter Eckersall]]), [[Bernard Kirk]] (selected by Walter Eckersall).<ref>1923 Michiganesian, p. 219.</ref>
*All-Conference: Harry Kipke, Bernard Kirk

==Coaching staff==
*Head coach: [[Fielding H. Yost]]
